__DESCRIPTION__

[Convos](http://convos.by/) is a modern IRC client for your browser, built in the [Mojolicious](http://mojolicio.us/) framework using HTML5 Web Technologies like Web Sockets, Desktop Notifications, Media Queries, and Push State. It's always on, storing your messages in a [Redis](http://redis.io/) backend even when you are not connected. In my presentation, I will go through some of our technology choices and challenges in building a fully asynchronous Node.js-like application in Perl. Updated and extended version.

[abstract](http://www.mojoconf.org/mojo2014/talk/5412)

